parti.","I contenuti sono integralmente coperti, in forma più estesa e ufficiale, dai due documenti separati Q20 Parte I (clausole 6.2 Personale e 6.3 Strutture/ambienti) e Q20 Parte II (clausole 6.4 Attrezzature, 6.6 Reagenti, 6.7 Accordi di servizio, 6.8 Servizi esterni), già ingeriti nella wiki.","Questa pagina viene mantenuta solo come riferimento bibliografico per evitare di perdere la citazione della fonte; per il contenuto tecnico-applicativo si rimanda alle pagine Q20 Parte I e Parte II e alle relative pagine concettuali."]},"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[]},"smart_blocks:Wiki/sources/SIPMeL - Accreditamento Personale Ambienti Attrezzature (versione previa).md#---frontmatter---": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"1rbsxas","at":1781675958833},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.05052749,0.01269932,0.00832962,0.03612487,-0.01004045,-0.06363325,-0.0206029,0.04332492,-0.0011337,-0.01281204,-0.03910549,-0.08466523,0.02549261,0.01043775,0.06473362,-0.01006334,0.02083091,0.03425719,0.03453662,-0.01829759,0.14490874,-0.01362408,-0.00453874,-0.05960134,-0.01286294,0.06108775,-0.01570937,-0.05642055,-0.04668569,-0.19620307,-0.00675854,0.04533703,0.02656262,-0.02933181,0.01353336,0.01184547,-0.03691204,0.0482681,0.01888061,0.0507801,0.07516801,0.06858633,0.00803697,-0.03013125,-0.02039782,-0.05329616,-0.01933276,0.04411341,-0.00319412,-0.03351128,-0.08573578,0.04172383,-0.01452888,0.07742765,0.01843251,0.04258616,0.05789969,-0.00491554,0.05804936,0.02103237,0.10446141,0.04638861,-0.2244499,0.06330522,0.01223344,0.023068,-0.06421187,-0.02337481,-0.05058798,-0.0300417,-0.05898598,-0.03945319,-0.00855954,0.03527831,0.04436634,-0.06285892,0.01407037,0.00823154,-0.02583193,-0.02841729,-0.00238754,0.04083508,-0.01985091,-0.0023083,0.00938615,-0.00033031,0.02725155,0.00086602,0.02593895,-0.00134757,-0.05561344,-0.09271707,0.07118343,0.05020284,0.02326958,0.00374549,-0.00526412,0.02246117,-0.03118929,0.08029769,-0.0221871,-0.01139962,-0.0334685,-0